sentences.english: But high taxes do not always mean expensive cigarettes.

sentences.english: He always has unattainable goals in his mind.
sentences.chinese: 他的脑子里总是想一些高不可攀的目标。

sentences.english: Only about twenty meters in height, but in my eyes is too high to be reached to the peak.
sentences.chinese: 大约只有二十米高，但在我眼中却是高不可攀的险峰。

sentences.english: Picasso's art is caviare to the general.
sentences.chinese: 毕加索的艺术，是一般大众高不可攀的东西。

sentences.english: Unreachable towers protrude upwards from the dusty, earthy surface.
sentences.chinese: 高不可攀的塔从尘土飞扬的泥土表面伸出来。

sentences.english: High-flown and amazing will come in due time.
sentences.chinese: 必要的时候，高不可攀和令人惊讶会出现。
